dets will lead discussions for the topic they present  A term paper involving testing an original hypothesis and using results compiled from published research literature will be written on a specific area of interest in biology  For the hands on research format  students will conduct original research and will write a research paper presenting their results  Note  Writing Intensive  W  Prerequisite s  Completion of one of the following courses prior to enrolling  BI 311  BI 312  BI 313  BI 325 BI 326  BI 335  or BI 430    Back to Top   Print Friendly Page   All catalogues   2016 Virginia Military Institute  Powered by the Acalog  Academic Catalog Management System   ACMS  Mobile Site 